{"title_page": "The Metal Mass \u2013 Live", "text_new": "{{Infobox album\n| name         = The Metal Mass \u2013 Live\n| type         = video\n| artist       = [[Powerwolf]]\n| cover        = Powerwolf - The Metal Mass - Live.jpg\n| alt          = \n| released     = 27 July 2016 (Japan)<br />29 July 2016 (Europe)\n| recorded     = 11 July 2015 ([[Masters of Rock (festival)|Masters of Rock]])<br />14 August 2015 ([[Summer Breeze Open Air]])<br />2 October 2015 (Turbinenhalle [[Oberhausen]])\n| venue        = \n| genre        = {{hlist|[[Power metal]]|[[Heavy metal music|heavy metal]]|[[speed metal]]}}\n| length       = \n| label        = {{hlist|[[Napalm Records]] (Europe)|Soyuz Music (Russia)|Chaos Reigns (Japan)}}\n| director     = Ville Lipi\u00e4nen\n| producer     = \n| prev_title   = [[Blessed & Possessed]]\n| prev_year    = 2015\n| next_title   = [[Preaching at the Breeze]]\n| next_year    = 2017\n| chronology   = \n| misc         = \n}}\n'''''The Metal Mass \u2013 Live''''' is the second video album by German [[power metal]] band [[Powerwolf]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.laut.de/Powerwolf/Alben/The-Metal-Mass-Live-100169|title=Metal, Blasphemie und gro\u00dfe Gesten.|website=laut.de|language=de|access-date=2019-08-26}}</ref> The album contains live footage of three shows: [[Masters of Rock (festival)|Masters of Rock 2015]], [[Summer Breeze Open Air|Summer Breeze 2015]], [[Oberhausen]] Turbinenhalle, music videos to \"[[Amen & Attack]]\", \"[[Army Of The Night]]\", \"[[We Drink Your Blood]]\" and \"[[Sanctified With Dynamite]]\", a festival documentation \"A Day At Summer Breeze\" and a tour documentation movie \"Kreuzweg \u2013 Of Wolves And Men\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.empik.com/the-metal-mass-live-powerwolf,p1127066975,muzyka-p|title=The Metal Mass Live|website=www.empik.com|language=pl|access-date=2019-08-22}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.metal-hammer.de/reviews/powerwolf-the-metal-mass-live/|title=Kritik zu Powerwolf The Metal Mass Live|website=Metal Hammer|language=de-DE|access-date=2019-08-26}}</ref>\n\nThe album was announced on 30 May 2016.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.blabbermouth.net/news/powerwolf-teaser-for-the-metal-mass-live-dvdblu-ray/|title=POWERWOLF: Teaser For 'The Metal Mass Live' DVD/Blu-Ray|last=Blabbermouth|date=2016-05-30|website=BLABBERMOUTH.NET|access-date=2019-08-26}}</ref>\n\n== Track listing ==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = DVD 1: Masters of Rock 2015 Show\n| title_width = 65%\n| collapsed = no\n| title1 = Sanctified With Dynamite\n| title2 = Coleus Sanctus\n| title3 = [[Army of the Night]]\n| title4 = [[Amen & Attack]]\n| title5 = Resurrection By Erection\n| title6 = [[Armata Strigoi]]\n| title7 = Sacred & Wild\n| title8 = All We Need Is Blood\n| title9 = Drumsolo\n| all_writing = \n| title10 = Kreuzfeuer\n| title11 = Werewolves of Armenia\n| title12 = We Drink Your Blood\n| title13 = Lupus Dei\n| title14 = Raise Your Fist, Evangelist\n| title15 = In The Name Of God (Deus Vult)\n| length1 = \n| length2 = \n| length3 = \n| length4 = \n| length5 = \n| length6 = \n| length7 = \n| length8 = \n| length9 = \n| length10 = \n| total_length = \n}}\n{{Track listing\n| headline = DVD 2: Summer Breeze 2015 Show\n| title_width = 65%\n| collapsed = no\n| title1 = Sanctified With Dynamite\n| title2 = Coleus Sanctus\n| title3 = [[Army of the Night]]\n| title4 = [[Amen & Attack]]\n| title5 = Resurrection By Erection\n| title6 = [[Armata Strigoi]]\n| title7 = Kreuzfeuer\n| title8 = Werewolves of Armenia\n| title9 = In The Name Of God (Deus Vult)\n| all_writing = \n| title10 = Blessed & Possessed\n| title11 = All We Need Is Blood\n| title12 = Dead Boys Don\u2018t Cry\n| title13 = We Drink Your Blood\n| title14 = Lupus Dei\n| title15 = In The Name Of God (Deus Vult)\n| length1 = \n| length2 = \n| length3 = \n| length4 = \n| length5 = \n| length6 = \n| length7 = \n| length8 = \n| length9 = \n| length10 = \n| total_length = \n}}\n{{Track listing\n| headline = DVD 3: Wolfsn\u00e4chte Tour 2