a|5|artist=Powerwolf|album=The+Metal+Mass+-+Live+%5BDVD%5D}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Netherlands|16|artist=Powerwolf|album=The+Metal+Mass+-+Live+%5BDVD%5D}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|2|artist=Powerwolf|refname=xyzzy|album=The-Metal-Mass-Live-%5BDVD%5D}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|5|artist=Powerwolf|refname=plugh|album=The+Metal+Mass+-+Live+%5BDVD%5D}}\n|}\n\n=== CD ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2019)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br /> position\n|-\n{{albumchart|Germany4|4|id=309151|artist=Powerwolf|album=The Metal Mass \u2013 Live}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Switzerland|30|artist=Powerwolf|album=The Metal Mass - Live}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|159|artist=Powerwolf|album=The Metal Mass - Live}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|79|artist=Powerwolf|album=The Metal Mass - Live}}\n|}\n\n== Release history ==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Region\n! scope=\"col\"| Date\n! scope=\"col\"| Format\n!Label\n! scope=\"col\"| Edition(s)\n! scope=\"col\"| Catalog\n! scope=\"col\" | {{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n! rowspan=\"5\" scope=\"row\" | Japan\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 27 July 2016\n| 2 Blu-rays\n| rowspan=\"5\" |Chaos Reigns\n| rowspan=\"4\" | Limited edition, Japan\n| rowspan=\"2\" | GQXS-90136-7\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.metal-archives.com/albums/Powerwolf/The_Metal_Mass_-_Live/786819|title=Powerwolf - The Metal Mass - Live - Encyclopaedia Metallum: The Metal Archives|website=www.metal-archives.com|access-date=2019-08-26}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2 DVD\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.metal-archives.com/albums/Powerwolf/The_Metal_Mass_-_Live/786818|title=Powerwolf - The Metal Mass - Live - Encyclopaedia Metallum: The Metal Archives|website=www.metal-archives.com|access-date=2019-08-26}}</ref>\n|-\n|CD + 2 DVD\n| rowspan=\"2\" |GQBS-90153-5\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.metal-archives.com/albums/Powerwolf/The_Metal_Mass_-_Live/786817|title=Powerwolf - The Metal Mass - Live - Encyclopaedia Me