\n\n{{Powerwolf}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:The Metal Mass - Live}}\n[[Category:Powerwolf live albums]]\n[[Category:2016 video albums]]\n[[Category:Live video albums]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox album\n| name         = The Metal Mass \u2013 Live\n| type         = video\n| artist       = [[Powerwolf]]\n| cover        = Powerwolf - The Metal Mass - Live.jpg\n| alt          = \n| released     = 27 July 2016 (Japan)<br />29 July 2016 (Europe)\n| recorded     = 11 July 2015 ([[Masters of Rock (festival)|Masters of Rock]])<br />14 August 2015 ([[Summer Breeze Open Air]])<br />2 October 2015 (Turbinenhalle [[Oberhausen]])\n| venue        = \n| genre        = {{hlist|[[Power metal]]|[[Heavy metal music|heavy metal]]|[[speed metal]]}}\n| length       = \n| label        = {{hlist|[[Napalm Records]] (Europe)|Soyuz Music (Russia)|Chaos Reigns (Japan)}}\n| director     = Ville Lipi\u00e4nen\n| producer     = \n| prev_title   = [[Blessed & Possessed]]\n| prev_year    = 2015\n| next_title   = [[Preaching at the Breeze]]\n| next_year    = 2017\n| chronology   = \n| misc         = \n}}\n'''''The Metal Mass \u2013 Live''''' is the second video album by German [[power metal]] band [[Powerwolf]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.laut.de/Powerwolf/Alben/The-Metal-Mass-Live-100169|title=Metal, Blasphemie und gro\u00dfe Gesten.|website=laut.de|language=de|access-date=2019-08-26}}</ref> The album contains live footage of three shows: [[Masters of Rock (festival)|Masters of Rock 2015]], [[Summer Breeze Open Air|Summer Breeze 2015]], [[Oberhausen]] Turbinenhalle, music videos to \"[[Amen & Attack]]\", \"[[Army Of The Night]]\", \"[[We Drink Your Blood]]\" and \"[[Sanctified With Dynamite]]\", a festival documentation \"A Day At Summer Breeze\" and a tour documentation movie \"Kreuzweg \u2013 Of Wolves And Men\".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.empik.com/the-metal-mass-live-powerwolf,p1127066975,muzyka-p|title=The Metal Mass Live|website=www.empik.com|language=pl|access-date=2019-08-22}}</ref><ref>{{Cite 